extends layout
block content
        .container.overlay#start
            h1 Stay Fresh
            // p.lead A boilerplate for Node.js web applications
            p Keep track of your pantry
        a(href="/shopping_list").container.overlay#list
            h2 Create your shopping list
        .container.overlay#description
            h2 About the website
            p This is a website to help you keep track of all the food you buy and make sure you finish foods that are about to expire. With foods that are about to expire, we also provide tons of delicious recipes you can try out to finish them up. After you have finished them up, remove them from the pantry list. You can also make your grocery shopping lists here by seeing what you're running low on!
